<paragraph blockId="51.[151,1436,944,1224]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Biology: Unknown; probably carrion scavengers in forests; the only species known was collected in a cave (probably a troglophile, because no troglomorphisms were recorded).</paragraph>
